You have done an excellant job, I have followed your work since early on and needless to say it's because of the things you have done with computers that have made me want to be like you. I'm glad you are happy with Doom 3, I purchsed it the day it came out and am simply amazed with the results you have produced, congradulations and I cannot wait until i see the fruits of your labor for this final engine!</div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_9909238">
[ <a href="//slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=116699&amp;threshold=1&amp;commentsort=0&amp;mode=thread&amp;cid=9876672">Parent</a>
